animeDescription: Lolita Anime was made on base of manga by Aki Uchiyama.Lolita Anime Vol.1 : Uchiyama Aki no Obyoki Aki-chanLolita Anime Vol.2 : Milk Nomi NingyoLolita Anime Vol.3 : Uchiyama Aki no Omorashi GokkoNote: There is another series titled "Lolita Anime." but it was made a little bit earlier.
